[{"Code":"en","Title":"[Internal] Entity Type Update Logic","Slug":"internal-entity-change","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mkggax5m-h1rjsn-035\"></p><div text=\"Loading text...\"><p data-block-id=\"mkm69xgx-b8jzsu-002\"></p></div><p data-block-id=\"mkggax5m-h1rjsn-035\"><img data-block-id=\"mkm4dmjw-m7noar-002\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(184).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"mkggax5m-pgcx2i-036\">⚠️ Limitations</h3><ul data-block-id=\"mkghdcbu-inonxs-330\" data-list-format=\"disc\"><li data-block-id=\"mkghdcbu-aw1id0-331\"><p data-block-id=\"mkggax5m-pgcx2i-036\">We only allow changing business entity types in the same country</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkghdcbu-aw1id0-331\"><p data-block-id=\"mkggax5m-pgcx2i-036\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"color:inherit;font-size:1rem;\">For V3, we do not allow switching to foreign entities</span></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkghdcbu-aw1id0-331\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontSize:1rem;\"><p data-block-id=\"mkggax5m-pgcx2i-036\"><span type=\"spanMark\" style=\"color:inherit;font-size:1rem;\">We will not clear business registration documents; they will remain in the KYC data even though the business entity type does not require it anymore.</span></p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mkgh78ar-mq7lst-196\">Individuals → Entity</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1296\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1296px;width:1296px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:1296px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"1296\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh8l1r-fyz2xl-216\">The following fields are cleared from the existing individual when it changes into an entity as the new entity-type does not have/require the corresponding fields.</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"1296\"><ul data-block-id=\"mkgh8wmx-l604nu-226\" data-list-format=\"disc\"><li data-block-id=\"mkgh8wmy-oa2pyl-227\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh8l1r-lf8cbj-221\"><strong>Bank Account Proof</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"27\">business_bank_account_document</code>)<span class=\"comment\" type=\"spanMark\"> </span></p><ul data-block-id=\"mkgh8wmx-l604nu-226\" data-list-format=\"circle\"><li data-block-id=\"mkgh8wmy-oa2pyl-227\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh8l1r-lf8cbj-221\"><span class=\"comment\" type=\"spanMark\"><em>PS: Thailand non-profit does not have this document</em></span></p></li></ul></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mkgh96jd-5kt0sa-228\">Entity → Individuals </h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1296\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1296px;width:1296px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:1296px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"1296\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh96jd-4lkowt-229\">The following fields are cleared from the existing entity when it changes into an individual as the new individual-type does not have the corresponding fields.</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"1296\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-vna8rc-239\"><strong>General Legal Information</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-rqvlla-240\" data-list-format=\"disc\"><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-6ju7c9-241\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-yz3whm-242\"><strong>Business Registration Number</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"27\">business_registration_number</code>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-jk8l2t-243\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-nbzied-244\"><strong>Business Legal Name</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"27\">business_legal_name</code>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-ons1sk-245\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-lft5x4-246\"><strong>Legal Entity Address</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"26\">legal_entity_address</code>)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-lft5x4-246\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-cgh278-247\"><strong>General Contact Information</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-ywqa1i-248\" data-path-to-node=\"2\"><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-imy1kg-249\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-p41ntw-250\" data-path-to-node=\"2,0,0\"><strong>Contact Person First Name</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"27\">contact_person_first_name</code>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-3xwjuw-251\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-88g98w-252\" data-path-to-node=\"2,1,0\"><strong>Contact Person Last Name</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"26\">contact_person_last_name</code>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-k7uen5-253\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti7-0fut4a-254\" data-path-to-node=\"2,2,0\"><strong>Contact Person Email</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"22\">contact_person_email_address</code>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-ys0ieg-255\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-6amrfz-256\" data-path-to-node=\"2,3,0\"><strong>Contact Person Mobile Code</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"28\">contact_person_mobile_country_code</code>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-u9nr72-257\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-p6h4h7-258\" data-path-to-node=\"2,4,0\"><strong>Contact Person Mobile Number</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,4,0\" data-index-in-node=\"30\">contact_person_mobile_number_only</code>)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-p6h4h7-258\" data-path-to-node=\"2,4,0\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-lzljan-259\"><strong>Stakeholders</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-4wu5hz-260\" data-path-to-node=\"2\"><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-jl211j-261\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-ip3m4i-262\"><strong>All Stakeholders </strong><span class=\"comment\" type=\"spanMark\">(entire array)</span></p><ul data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-iaqtm7-263\" data-path-to-node=\"2\"><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-7qt2kv-264\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-227p86-265\">⚠️ Take note!! all stakeholders will be cleared when we migrate as individual-type does not have stakeholders</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-lb00vs-266\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-9gvbfh-267\" data-path-to-node=\"4,0,0\"><strong>Board Resolution</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"4,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"18\">authorized_person_board_resolution_document</code>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-8zm6mf-268\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-3lwe5n-269\" data-path-to-node=\"4,1,0\"><strong>Corporate Shareholder Indicator</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"4,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"33\">shareholders_include_corporate_entity</code>)</p><ul data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-sgnjr0-270\" data-path-to-node=\"2\"><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-hibchi-271\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-9d4szl-272\" data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0\">Y/N question whether their shareholding chart contains corporate entities</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-gw1dfv-273\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-p4d3u9-274\" data-path-to-node=\"4,2,0\"><strong>Shareholding Chart</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"4,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">business_shareholding_chart_document</code>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-mfeb29-275\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-2iu8fh-276\" data-path-to-node=\"4,3,0\"><strong>Letter of Authorization</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"4,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"25\">authorized_person_letter_of_authorization_document</code>)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-2iu8fh-276\" data-path-to-node=\"4,3,0\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-jd1bom-277\"><strong>Country Specific Docs</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-j33xe3-278\" data-path-to-node=\"6\"><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-mmpdm3-279\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-wgnded-280\" data-path-to-node=\"6,0,0\"><strong>Bank Account Proof</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"6,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">business_bank_account_document</code>) <em>— Thailand Only</em></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-nkhg8a-281\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-vvvit6-282\" data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0\"><strong>Amended Registration Docs</strong> <strong>Checkbox </strong>(<code data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"27\">business_registration_documents_amended</code>) <em>— Indonesia &amp; Mexico Only</em></p><ul data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-we1r69-283\" data-path-to-node=\"6\"><li data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-w5yiso-284\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mkgh9ti8-c8timj-285\" data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0\">Y/N question whether they had changed their business registration docs since incorporating</p></li></ul></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mkghaih1-hakx6y-294\">Entity → Entity</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1296\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1296px;width:1296px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:1296px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"1296\"><p data-block-id=\"mkghayfj-jptoq0-299\">The following fields are cleared from the existing entity when it changes into another entity-type as some information are unable to map to the new corresponding field requirements.</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"1296\"><p data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-s3dabw-289\"><strong>Stakeholders</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-qacn5u-287\" data-list-format=\"disc\"><li data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-l58j1c-288\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-s3dabw-289\"><strong>Stakeholder Roles Only</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"24\">stakeholders</code>)</p><ul data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-qacn5u-287\" data-list-format=\"circle\"><li data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-l58j1c-288\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-s3dabw-289\">⚠️ Take note!! all stakeholders roles will be cleared when we migrate as entity→entity have differing stakeholder role requirements</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-l58j1c-288\"><p data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-s3dabw-289\">e.g. Partnership has legal_partners, while Corporations has board_directors</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-l58j1c-288\"><p data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-s3dabw-289\"><strong>Board Resolution</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"18\">authorized_person_board_resolution_document</code>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-l58j1c-288\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-s3dabw-289\"><strong>Corporate Shareholder Indicator</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"33\">shareholders_include_corporate_entity</code>)</p><ul data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-qacn5u-287\" data-list-format=\"circle\"><li data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-l58j1c-288\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-s3dabw-289\">Y/N question whether their shareholding chart contains corporate entitie</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-l58j1c-288\"><p data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-s3dabw-289\"><strong>Shareholding Chart</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">business_shareholding_chart_document</code>)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-l58j1c-288\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold;\"><p data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-s3dabw-289\"><strong>Letter of Authorization</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,4,0\" data-index-in-node=\"25\">authorized_person_letter_of_authorization_document</code>)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-s3dabw-289\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mkghad8t-s3dabw-289\"><strong>Country Specific Docs</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mkghb7pd-2zluq9-322\"><li data-block-id=\"mkghb7pd-z9xyyd-323\"><p data-block-id=\"mkghb7pd-5klgdf-324\" data-path-to-node=\"2,5,0\"><strong>Bank Account Proof</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,5,0\" data-index-in-node=\"20\">business_bank_account_document</code>) <em>— Thailand Only</em></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mkghb7pd-w9vc6l-325\"><p data-block-id=\"mkghb7pd-95scd1-326\" data-path-to-node=\"2,6,0\"><strong>Amended Registration Docs</strong> (<code data-path-to-node=\"2,6,0\" data-index-in-node=\"27\">business_registration_documents_amended</code>) <em>— Indonesia &amp; Mexico Only</em></p></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mkgh7b34-z4a606-202\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mkgh2oi0-p6emzy-179\">Sample Migration</h2><p data-block-id=\"mkghc9ie-yfjkep-328\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mkgh3r3i-w7sy0g-181\"></p>","SeoTitle":"[Internal] Entity Type Update Logic","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"[Internal] Entity Change","Slug":"internal-entity-change","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"[Internal] Entity Change","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"[Internal] Entity Change","Slug":"internal-entity-change","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"[Internal] Entity Change","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"[Internal] Entity Change","Slug":"internal-entity-change","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"[Internal] Entity Change","Description":null}]